thelocal.de/20170103/bavaria-must-remain-part-of-germany-says-top-court</a><br />\n同Washington post <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/01/04/a-german-court-has-shut-down-hopes-for-a-breakaway-bavaria/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fworldviews%2Fwp%2F2017%2F01%2F04%2Fa-german-court-has-shut-down-hopes-for-a-breakaway-bavaria%2F&d=eWIWh0ev6rHAwRz%2FCIq26Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=96ced4ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/01/04/a-german-court-has-shut-down-hopes-for-a-breakaway-bavaria/</a></blockquote><br />\n有正常網頁唔post，走去post content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所謂「本文轉自：DJY」，原文條link又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n垃圾content farm宣傳者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜鬼嘢Contact farm啫<br />\n事實上係有就有，你要認為係fakenews 咁都冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847fcd34b573ee6dd39997678288b7f76082ba65","tid":421213,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"點解英國可以自古以嚟就咁撚大方<br />\n放走幾百個殖民地<br />\n蘇格蘭獨立又俾佢公投，仲要畀兩次<br />\n其他國家就驚到瀨屎"},{"pid":"104485c332bfb324f51fb6882c2f71369ed4f136","tid":421213,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解英國可以自古以嚟就咁撚大方<br />\n放走幾百個殖民地<br />\n蘇格蘭獨立又俾佢公投，仲要畀兩次<br />\n其他國家就驚到瀨屎</blockquote><br />\n因為英格蘭人知道有勝算先畀蘇格蘭公投啫，其實係賭㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似魁北克咁"},{"pid":"49090a84db4694803c07ee258f33a35a7b000b5d","tid":421213,"uid":80624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分番開做普魯士is ok</blockquote><br />\n普魯士已經唔再存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af63fcd1fd1a156616f46b8f25f0760a466d1c2","tid":421213,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分番開做普魯士is ok</blockquote><br />\n普魯士已經唔再存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n康尼斯堡已經變咗做俄佬地方，有德國色彩嘅嘢已經清除得七七八八。西普魯士行省都冇埋，而家嘅德國唯一同普魯士同德意志有關嘅得返霍亨索倫家族嘅後人，仲掛住個虛名嘅普魯士親王<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7d83e747cd4585cb85aa9156411a9e2228477a","tid":421213,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"巴伐利亞係德意志帝國最後合併嘅地方之一，巴伐利亞仲要係中世紀後德語系國家中誕生好多出色嘅哲學家軍事人物，一戰佢係德國最有傳統文化色彩嘅地區，二戰佢亦係納粹黨嘅發跡地，巴伐利亞嘅存在根本就係近代德國史不可或缺嘅一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當巴伐利亞真係獨立成國，直頭意味德國正式成為歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b7312407b6d92a8742f016ab5638f9643d3dd8","tid":421213,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"preussen gloria <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a2d8f278159aa9fbdadc41d27ef228e39212e8","tid":421213,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分番開做普魯士is ok</blockquote><br />\n普魯士已經唔再存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最東北部唔係普魯士咩"},{"pid":"11b7d09696d4627798ba69c2038617bae4f00e3c","tid":421213,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分番開做普魯士is ok</blockquote><br />\n普魯士已經唔再存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最東北部唔係普魯士咩</blockquote><br />\nno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Meckenburg-Vorpommern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5738f707a145d6ea16a65a67c202a513958cadb4","tid":421213,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分番開做普魯士is ok</blockquote><br />\n普魯士已經唔再存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最東北部唔係普魯士咩</blockquote><br />\n普魯士係喺波蘭東北部x俄羅斯加里寧格勒州x立陶宛克萊佩達南部(小立陶宛）"},{"pid":"cf2825ab2f1e6592ea104fb3e0b5b6ea0e447a62","tid":421213,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}